<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-1')">1</a>. But he didn’t know my name then. He just asked me for a light.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. This isn’t a memory. That sniper’s bullet must have cracked my helmet and let him in.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-3"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-3')">3</a>. I try to think about Harriet &#8212; the mission &#8212; my dead comrades. Their names bubble into my mind &#8212; then a twisting, wrenching ache stretches down the side of my head into my arms. I retreat instinctively to the safety of Anwar’s mind game.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-4"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-4')">4</a>. Anwar always did have softer sheets than me.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-5"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-5')">5</a>. I hope the pride in my voice comes through. Can’t tell in a flashback &#8212; even one this twisted.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-6"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-6')">6</a>. I’d never been here before but had heard rave reviews about the coffee; it seemed like the perfect place to plead for Anwar’s life.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-7"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-7')">7</a>. All I remember from that day is Anwar, and his fate in my hands.</div>
</div>

